videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald lobs a pass to WR Stephen Guidry, who makes a leaping catch in the end zone while keeping a foot inbounds.
videos.headline: Guidry makes incredible TD catch

videos.description: Texas A&M QB Kellen Mond tosses a quick short pass to WR Quartney Davis, who flies 34 yards into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Davis speeds into end zone for TD

videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald sends a 38-yard pass into the end zone to WR Osirus Mitchell, who makes the leaping grab for the score.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald finds Mitchell in the end zone for TD

videos.description: On third-and-21, Nick Fitzgerald finds Stephen Guidry for 84 yards, pinning Mississippi State on the two-yard line.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald connects with Guidry on big play

videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald calls his own number and powers forward for a one-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald keeps it himself for the score

videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald goes with the keeper, finds a hole and sprints 76 yards for a touchdown to widen the Bulldogs' lead.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald breaks loose for 76-yard TD

videos.description: Mississippi State head coach Joe Moorhead praises the peformance of his QB Nick Fitzgerald after beating Texas A&M 28-13.
videos.headline: Moorhead is 'proud as hell' of Nick Fitzgerald
